734
00:59:29,100 --> 00:59:31,100
Well, let's see.

735
00:59:31,900 --> 00:59:35,800
Yes. That's very good.
It's coming along quite nicely.

736
00:59:36,100 --> 00:59:39,600
I've been asking your man for a mirror.
He can't seem to find one for me.

737
00:59:39,900 --> 00:59:43,900
- Oh, well... Lupo, mirror?
- I can't find one anywhere.

738
00:59:44,100 --> 00:59:48,700
After application of all your techniques,
I'm terribly anxious to check my progress.

739
00:59:49,000 --> 00:59:51,200
- Yes, of course.
- Yes.

740
00:59:51,400 --> 00:59:54,100
