746
01:00:12,100 --> 01:00:13,400
Yes.

747
01:00:13,500 --> 01:00:16,600
- Good. Bad weather or some such?
- Yes. Of course I did.

748
01:00:16,800 --> 01:00:19,900
What of Francesca? I told her
I'd take her to the carnival ball,

749
01:00:20,100 --> 01:00:22,900
but I do think I need just a bit more time.

750
01:00:23,100 --> 01:00:26,100
Yes, I think you're right.
You do need some more time.

751
01:00:26,400 --> 01:00:28,800
- Listen. Don't worry. I'll handle that.
- Good man.

752
01:00:29,000 --> 01:00:31,500
