756
01:00:43,200 --> 01:00:47,000
My name is Bernardo Guardi,
but I'm not the Bernardo Guardi.

757
01:00:47,300 --> 01:00:52,000
Come along now, Bernardo.
There's no shame in being a writer.

758
01:00:52,300 --> 01:00:54,600
Let's play a little game, shall we?

759
01:00:54,800 --> 01:00:56,900
I'll read you a sentence and you finish it.

760
01:00:57,100 --> 01:00:59,600
"A woman is air and... "

761
01:00:59,800 --> 01:01:01,900
And what, Bernardo?

762
01:01:02,100 --> 01:01:06,700
I don't know. Trouble?
No. No.

763
01:01:07,000 --> 01:01:08,800
Wind? Air and wind?

764
01:01:09,000 --> 01:01:12,800
No. I'll give you a little clue, shall I?

765
01:01:16,800 --> 01:01:19,900
It's not the tea I object to.
It's the water.

766
01:01:21,000 --> 01:01:25,600
So, Signor Papprizzio,
how well do you know Casanova?

767
01:01:28,100 --> 01:01:30,700
Be careful how you answer.

768
01:01:30,900 --> 01:01:33,700
I could become interested in you.

769
01:01:37,600 --> 01:01:39,400
I was less than...

770
01:01:39,600 --> 01:01:43,300
