did you go with Casanova to his house?

774
01:01:55,400 --> 01:01:57,800
- I'm renting it from him.
- You're renting it?

775
01:01:58,000 --> 01:02:00,700
- It's strictly business, of course.
- Business.

776
01:02:00,800 --> 01:02:03,600
I believe he went
out of town for a day or two.

777
01:02:03,900 --> 01:02:06,000
- Out of town?
- Yes.

778
01:02:07,400 --> 01:02:12,900
Well, if I know anything, he's hardly
likely to absent himself from Carnevale.

779
01:02:14,300 --> 01:02:20,600
Signor Papprizzio, if you'd help put an end
to this fornicator's career for good and all,

780
01:02:20,800 --> 01:02:24,800
believe me, the Church
will be very grateful.

781
01:02:25,000 --> 01:02:26,900
How grateful?

782
01:02:27,100 --> 01:02:29,300
The lard concession at the Vatican.

783
01:02:29,500 --> 01:02:32,800
Which is a lot of lard.

784
01:02:34,000 --> 01:02:36,200
That's quite an attractive offer.

785
01:02:36,400 --> 01:02:38,400
So we have a deal?

786
01:02:38,600 --> 01:02:41,900
You will help deliver Casanova unto me?

787
01:02:42,100 --> 01:02:44,000
As sure as my name is Papprizzio.

788
01:02:45,000 --> 01:02:46,900
- Excuse me, Your Reverence.
- No.

789
01:02:47,100 --> 01:02:51,100
This Bernardo Guardi we're racking,
I don't think he is the heretic.

790
01:02:51,400 --> 01:02:54,100
I think someone is just using his name

791
01:02:54,300 --> 01:02:56,700
- as a nom de plume.
- A nom...

792
01:02:56,900 --> 01:02:59,600
Don't be clever, Andolini.
What do you mean you think?

793
01:02:59,800 --> 01:03:02,200
The Inquisition is not paid to think. Be sure!

794
01:03:02,300 --> 01:03:06,600
Well, I am pretty sure.
He can't read or write.

795
01:03:09,600 --> 01:03:12,400
Lupo! Lupo!

796
01:03:13,800 --> 01:03:16,800
- There is no lover!
- What?

797
01:03:16,900 --> 01:03:18,700
- There is no secret lover.
- What?

798
01:03:18,900 --> 01:03:21,000
She never had one.

799
01:03:28,200 --> 01:03:30,100
Carnevale.

800
01:03:58,900 --> 01:04:00,900
Talked of pigs all week.

801
01:04:01,100 --> 01:04:04,200
- Darling, have you seen my husband?
- I am your husband.

802
01:04:04,400 --> 01:04:09,300
