- I don't know what he looks like.

803
01:04:09,600 --> 01:04:13,700
But he's bound to be here.
He wouldn't miss the carnival.

804
01:04:14,000 --> 01:04:15,900
Signor Papprizzio.

805
01:04:17,000 --> 01:04:19,900
See? Everybody's here.
We just have to find them.

806
01:04:54,000 --> 01:04:55,900
Victoria?

807
01:05:00,200 --> 01:05:02,000
Victoria!

808
01:05:07,300 --> 01:05:08,900
Good evening, sir.

809
01:05:18,000 --> 01:05:20,100
Signor Pizzani and Signora.

810
01:05:20,200 --> 01:05:22,200
You're welcome.

811
01:05:24,600 --> 01:05:28,000
Signor Papprizzio of Genoa
escorting Signorina Bruni.

812
01:05:28,100 --> 01:05:30,100
You're welcome.

813
01:05:34,800 --> 01:05:38,100
Signor Dandolo and Signora.

