01:05:38,300 --> 01:05:39,500
You're welcome.

815
01:05:47,700 --> 01:05:49,800
- Signor Papprizzio.
- Mother Bruni.

816
01:05:50,000 --> 01:05:52,200
We must introduce you
to everyone we know.

817
01:05:52,400 --> 01:05:53,900
Yes, this should be interesting.

818
01:05:54,000 --> 01:05:56,200
- Will you do me the honor, signora?
- May I?

819
01:05:56,400 --> 01:05:58,600
- Well, I'm free.
- I...

820
01:05:58,800 --> 01:06:01,600
- Be my guest.
- Watch this.

821
01:06:07,100 --> 01:06:09,800
Signor Casanova,
I have a message from your fiancée.

822
01:06:10,000 --> 01:06:12,800
- Ah, which one?
- Signorina Donato.

823
01:06:13,100 --> 01:06:16,500
She's in the piazza.
She's waiting for you to escort her in.

824
01:06:16,700 --> 01:06:18,700
Good Lord!

825
01:06:36,400 --> 01:06:38,300
Come.

826
01:06:48,800 --> 01:06:53,600
Don't worry.
You're not my first virgin.

827
01:06:55,800 --> 01:06:58,100
- Victoria.
- Casanova.

828
01:07:04,900 --> 01:07:07,800
Something is not right.

829
01:07:08,000 --> 01:07:12,100
Do we have the address
of Casanova's house?

830
01:07:12,400 --> 01:07:15,700
Then I think now is the time
for positive action.

831
01:07:15,900 --> 01:07:18,300
Lord and Lady Devonshire.

832
01:07:19,700 --> 01:07:21,000
You're welcome.

833
01:07:21,200 --> 01:07:23,600
Signor Casanova
and Signorina Donato.

834
01:07:25,700 --> 01:07:27,600
Signor Casanova.

835
01:07:27,800 --> 01:07:32,700
Enchanting.
I'm so very pleased for you and me.

836
01:07:33,000 --> 01:07:36,400
- When's the wedding?
- Soon, Your Grace.

837
01:07:36,700 --> 01:07:39,000
You're welcome.

838
01:07:40,100 --> 01:07:42,700
Ambassador Gritti and Signora.

839
01:07:54,000 --> 01:07:56,200
- My darling.
- Giacomo, where can we go?

840
01:07:56,400 --> 01:07:59,200
- Find somewhere.
- Find somewhere? No, no.

841
01:07:59,300 --> 01:08:03,800
- I can't wait any longer.
- Sit down. Very good.

842
01:08:04,100 --> 01:08:07,100
Wait here and I'll come back
with a glass of wine.

843
01:08:07,200 --> 01:08:10,600
- Casanova.
- How wonderful to see you.

844
01:08:32,600 --> 01:08:34,900
What are you doing down there? No.

845
01:08:44,600 --> 01:08:46,300
There he is.

846
01:08:48,000 --> 01:08:52,200
- We danced off our feet.
- You danced off your feet. How lovely.

847
01:08:58,300 --> 01:09:00,200
