852
01:09:14,100 --> 01:09:15,600
- May I?
- Please.

853
01:09:15,700 --> 01:09:16,700
Thank you.

854
01:09:19,100 --> 01:09:23,100
- You all right?
- Yeah, I'm fine. Just hot.

855
01:09:23,400 --> 01:09:25,900
- I didn't see you in church.
- Well, I was there.

856
01:09:26,100 --> 01:09:28,400
I know, but I wasn't.

857
01:09:32,100 --> 01:09:35,000
- Do you know Signor...
- Yes. I'm the future son-in-law.

858
01:09:35,200 --> 01:09:37,400
- That's right.
- Yes!

859
01:09:38,600 --> 01:09:41,000
- Congratulations are in order.
- Yes.

860
01:09:41,100 --> 01:09:44,000
Thank you.

861
01:09:44,200 --> 01:09:45,900
No. No, I mean...

862
01:09:46,100 --> 01:09:48,900
No. Yes. Congratulations are in order.

863
01:09:49,100 --> 01:09:50,600
I just said that.

864
01:09:55,100 --> 01:09:58,300
Congratulations.
You must be pleased for Victoria.

865
01:09:58,400 --> 01:10:01,100
That reminds me.
Have you seen Victoria?

866
01:10:04,100 --> 01:10:05,600
No, no. That's true.

867
01:10:05,800 --> 01:10:08,700
I thought she'd be here
with her... her fiance.

868
01:10:08,900 --> 01:10:12,000
That's true. I haven't seen her anywhere.
I think she's...

869
01:10:12,200 --> 01:10:15,000
I had forbidden her to come,
but she has defied me.

870
01:10:15,200 --> 01:10:17,700
- She must have changed.
- She has.

871
